<div class="rounded-lg bg-base-200/60 p-4 text-sm">
  <p class="font-medium">DNS setup</p>
  <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-1.5 pl-5 text-base-content/70">
    <li>
      <span class="font-medium text-base-content">Subdomain</span>
      (e.g. <code class="text-xs">app.example.com</code>): add a
      <span class="font-medium text-base-content">CNAME</span> pointing to
      <code class="text-xs"><%= AppHost.primary_host %></code>.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="font-medium text-base-content">Apex / root domain</span>
      (e.g. <code class="text-xs">example.com</code>): add an
      <span class="font-medium text-base-content">A</span> record pointing to
      <code class="text-xs"><%= AppHost.server_ip %></code>.
    </li>
  </ul>
</div>
